@host = http://localhost:5199

### Crear reserva (Premium, 5 pasajeros) -> 201 Created
POST {{host}}/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Juan Pérez",
  "origin": "Bogotá",
  "destination": "Aeropuerto El Dorado",
  "date": "2026-12-20T10:00:00",
  "passengers": 5,
  "serviceType": "premium"
}

### Obtener todas las reservas
GET {{host}}/reservations

### Obtener una reserva por id (reemplazar {id})
GET {{host}}/reservations/{id}

### Confirmar una reserva (reemplazar {id})
PATCH {{host}}/reservations/{id}/confirm

### Cancelar una reserva (reemplazar {id})
PATCH {{host}}/reservations/{id}/cancel

### Ejemplo de payload inválido -> 400 con errores por campo
POST {{host}}/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "",
  "origin": "Cali",
  "destination": "Cali",
  "date": "2020-01-01T10:00:00",
  "passengers": 9,
  "serviceType": "luxury"
}
